      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>377</span> - <span>Associated Language</span> (R)
      </h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Authority - full</div>
      <div class="datename">September 2011</div>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="indicators">
         <tr>
            <th width="45%"> First Indicator </th>
            <th width="45%"> Second Indicator </th>
         </tr>
         <tr>
            <td><em>Undefined</em><br /><span># - Undefined</span><br /><br /></td>
            <td><em>Source of code</em><br /><span># - MARC language code</span><br /><span>7 - Source specified in $2</span><br /><br /></td>
         </tr>
      </table>
      <hr />
      <table width="100%" class="subfields">
         <tr>
            <td width="50%"></td>
